<h1 align="center">
  MLV Web
</h1>

Personal Portfolio code for [www.micaela.rocks](https://www.micaela.rocks) created with Gatsby.js

## 🚀 Quick start

1.  **Run web**

    Use the Gatsby CLI to run the server by typing:

    ```
    gatsby develop
    ```
